<p>XRP is the native math-based currency of the Ripple network, which enables instant and nearly free payments in any currency based on the Ripple protocol. Ripple Labs (the team behind the Ripple network) created 100 billion XRP at Ripple’s inception. Because Ripple is a decentralized payment network and distributed currency exchange, Ripple Labs plans to freely give away at least 55% of the total XRP. Learn more at <a title="https://ripple.com/" href="https://ripple.com/" target="_blank">ripple.com</a>.</p>
